### Interaction and Disabled
Clickable tags can toggle lightweight state. Disabled tags block both `click` and `close`.
:::TuffDemoWrapper{demo="TagStateDemo" code-lang="vue"}
---
code: |
  <script setup>
  import { ref } from 'vue'

  const active = ref(false)
  </script>

  <template>
    <TxTag
      :label="active ? 'Selected' : 'Clickable'"
      :color="active ? 'var(--tx-color-success)' : 'var(--tx-color-primary)'"
      @click="active = !active"
    />
    <TxTag label="Disabled" disabled />
  </template>
---
:::

